tool_description: This API returns jokes about video games, gamers and more. New jokes are added monthly.
name: Game Jokes API
title: Game Jokes API

api_list.name: random-ten
api_list.description: Get 10 random jokes in form of an array.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://game-jokes-api.p.rapidapi.com/random-ten"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "game-jokes-api.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
